text: Alfredo del Mazo Maza (13 November 1975) was a Mexican politician. He was Governor of the State of Mexico from 2017 to 1923. For a brief time in 1994, he was President of the Institutional Revolutionary Party. Pichardo Pagaza was born in Toluca, State of Mexico, Mexico. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:People from Toluca Category:Governors of the State of Mexico Category:Mayors from Mexico (state)
title: Alfredo del Mazo Maza
